{{- /*
NetBird Kubernetes Operator values overlay.

The kubeaid netbird-operator chart is a wrapper: `netbird-operator:` is the
upstream operator subchart (where managementURL lives), while networkRouter /
networkResources / clusterProxy are TOP-LEVEL wrapper values consumed by the
chart's own CR templates (templates/{network-router,network-resources,
cluster-proxy}.yaml) — hence the differing indentation below.

managementURL points the operator at the parent NetBird Mgmt —
cluster.netbird.dns on VPN clusters (they host Mgmt themselves), the
netbird.<base> Keycloak-DNS convention on workload clusters. Omitting it is
NOT harmless: the operator binary falls back to NetBird Cloud (api.netbird.io),
so when the URL can't be derived this file omits it and the operator must be
wired manually. The Mgmt API token flows via the netbird-mgmt-api-key Secret,
not values (netbird.AwaitOperatorToken gates bootstrap on that Secret).

networkRouter + the traefik-internal networkResource are convention, not
config — rendered whenever a mesh DNS zone is set: the router registers the
cluster as a NetBird routing peer; the resource publishes the internal Traefik
to the mesh. dnsZoneRef is cluster.netbird.dnsZone, operator-chosen and
validated to differ from the control-plane/Mgmt domains because NetBird
rejects a zone that collides with a real service domain. The zone and the
k8s-<cluster> group (.NetBirdInternalIngressGroup) must already exist in
NetBird — created via the dashboard steps in printNetBirdOperatorInstructions.

clusterProxy (kubectl-over-mesh + RBAC) comes from cluster.netbird.clusterProxy;
the ClusterProxy CR is named after cluster.name.
*/ -}}
{{- if .NetBirdOperatorEnabled }}
{{- if .NetBirdManagementURL }}
netbird-operator:
  managementURL: {{ .NetBirdManagementURL | quote }}
{{- end }}
{{- if .NetBirdRouterEnabled }}
networkRouter:
  enabled: true
  dnsZone: {{ .NetBird.DNSZone | quote }}
  replicas: 1
networkResources:
  - name: traefik-internal
    namespace: traefik
    service: traefik-internal
    groups:
      - {{ .NetBirdInternalIngressGroup | quote }}
{{- end }}
{{- if .NetBirdClusterProxyEnabled }}
clusterProxy:
  enabled: true
  clusterName: {{ .ClusterConfig.Name | quote }}
{{- with .NetBird.ClusterProxy }}
{{- if gt (len .RBAC) 0 }}
  rbac:
{{- range .RBAC }}
    - group: {{ .Group | quote }}
      clusterRole: {{ .ClusterRole | quote }}
{{- end }}
{{- end }}
{{- end }}
{{- end }}
{{- end }}
